name: cosmicnouveau
description: Has a mind of its own. Just made it on around 25 images I generated, there were no text or artist names on them but I think I used way too many (32) tokens for the embedding and it insists on putting a tag in the bottom left in the images I have made with it so far. lol, also I changed the style text and I do not know what I am doing at all hardly quite yet. I suggest using art by (cosmicnouveau:0.3) above 0.5 it just does what it wants completely. Use under 15 cfg and rather high steps probably 45+ or who knows. Made the images on my own merge model neurocontrastdream but it has models that say not for commercial use in it so I assume the ti is also not for commercial use sorry.
